                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="1r" facs="002">Fols 1r–1r</locus>
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3985Mazmura#Psalm1">Mazmura
                                                  Dǝngǝl, Psalm1</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ነዓ፡ ኀቤየ፡ ዳዊት፡ ንጉሠ፡ እስራኤል። በዐለ፡ መዝሙር፡ ሠናይ፡ ወጥዑመ፡ ቃል። ታለብወኒ፡ ነገረ፡ ወፍካሬ፡ ኵሉ፡ አምሳል። ከመ፡ እሰድሳ፡ ለማርያም፡ ድንግል።</incipit>
                     <note>The Psalter is introduced with the first psalm of the Psalter of the Viring</note>
                     </msItem>

                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="1r" to="120r" facs="002">Fols 1r–120r</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur">Mazmura Dāwit</title>
                     </msItem>

